<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 20:05:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>挑衅的国际法院法官称以色列-加沙战争是“政治性的”，在世界法院没有地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/defiant-icj-judge-says-gaza-war-with-israel-is-political-and-has-no-place-in-world-court/0000018d-4ba5-d561-a5bd-6faff0060000</link><description>法官朱莉娅·塞布廷德在提交给联合国最高法院的少数意见中表示，“南非没有证明”以色列在加沙的行为“具有必要的种族灭绝意图”，因此符合《种族灭绝公约》的规定</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 17:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/defiant-icj-judge-says-gaza-war-with-israel-is-political-and-has-no-place-in-world-court/0000018d-4ba5-d561-a5bd-6faff0060000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯坚持结束战争，以色列官员对人质协议持悲观态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-pessimistic-about-hostage-deal-as-hamas-insists-on-end-to-war/0000018d-4baf-d561-a5bd-6faf1cf60000</link><description>哈马斯要求以色列完全撤军、国际社会保证结束战斗以及该组织重新控制加沙，这些都对达成协议构成了障碍。以色列高级官员表示，“就以色列而言，不可能为谈判创造一个起点”</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 17:13:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-pessimistic-about-hostage-deal-as-hamas-insists-on-end-to-war/0000018d-4baf-d561-a5bd-6faf1cf60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法律专家表示，国际法院法官基本上采纳了南非的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-legal-experts-say-icj-judges-largely-adopted-south-africas-narrative/0000018d-4bb7-d02c-a79f-4bbf16f60000</link><description>以色列人认为海牙法院没有成功下令停止加沙战争，但法院同意存在合理的种族灭绝风险</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 16:50:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-legal-experts-say-icj-judges-largely-adopted-south-africas-narrative/0000018d-4bb7-d02c-a79f-4bbf16f60000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯摇滚乐队 Bi-2 在泰国被捕，其中包括四名以色列成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/russian-rock-band-bi-2-including-four-israeli-members-arrested-in-thailand/0000018d-49d8-d35c-a39f-ebda2c790000</link><description>在公开表示反对乌克兰战争后，乐队担心俄罗斯是其被捕的幕后黑手</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 08:22:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/russian-rock-band-bi-2-including-four-israeli-members-arrested-in-thailand/0000018d-49d8-d35c-a39f-ebda2c790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人示威，呼吁立即举行选举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-live/yemens-houthis-say-they-attacked-a-british-ship-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-lebanon/0000018d-48c4-dc44-a5bf-c8f64edc0000</link><description>英国与美国和其他四个国家一起撤回对近东救济工程处的资助 ■ 美国和英国军队在英国油轮遇袭后袭击了红海胡塞武装 ■ 拜登与埃及、卡塔尔领导人通话，强调需要达成​​新的人质协议、延长停火协议-fire ■ 国际法院呼吁以色列减轻加沙人的苦难</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 03:35:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-live/yemens-houthis-say-they-attacked-a-british-ship-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-lebanon/0000018d-48c4-dc44-a5bf-c8f64edc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者找到了虐待巴勒斯坦牧羊人的新方法：让他们破产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-settlers-have-found-a-new-way-to-abuse-palestinian-shepherds-bankrupting-them/0000018d-4822-dc44-a5bf-c8b681660000</link><description>本周，警方扣押了 700 只羊，声称它们穿越了禁区。为了取回这些动物，牧羊人向定居者地区委员会支付了 150,000 谢克尔</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 00:21:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-settlers-have-found-a-new-way-to-abuse-palestinian-shepherds-bankrupting-them/0000018d-4822-dc44-a5bf-c8b681660000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列历史上最伟大的恐吓者”：内塔尼亚胡的恐吓策略如何操纵以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-one-generates-fear-like-him-how-netanyahus-scare-tactics-manipulate-israelis/0000018d-47c8-d02c-a79f-47db0d710000</link><description>乌里尔·阿布洛夫说，内塔尼亚胡权力的秘密在于滥用权力。作为恐惧政治的研究者，他试图理解我们如何才能爬出深渊，回到希望政治</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 23:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-one-generates-fear-like-him-how-netanyahus-scare-tactics-manipulate-israelis/0000018d-47c8-d02c-a79f-47db0d710000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称，他们被俘的儿子被哈马斯杀害。然后病理学家出现了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-their-captive-son-was-killed-by-hamas-then-a-pathologist-showed-up/0000018d-4756-d35c-a39f-ef5e4de10000</link><description>她的儿子被哈马斯扣为人质并在加沙被发现死亡，而对他尸体的尸检和有关他死亡的军方报告都没有结论，愤怒的马扬·谢尔曼要求以色列国防军和国家给出答案。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-their-captive-son-was-killed-by-hamas-then-a-pathologist-showed-up/0000018d-4756-d35c-a39f-ef5e4de10000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的人道主义灾难是国际法院对以色列种族灭绝裁决的核心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/gazan-humanitarian-crisis-overshadows-everything-else-in-icjs-preliminary-genocide-ruling/0000018d-4739-d02c-a79f-47bb34a90000</link><description>国际法院的临时裁决重点关注加沙最紧迫的问题：巴勒斯坦人的灾难性状况，以及释放以色列人质的必要性</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/gazan-humanitarian-crisis-overshadows-everything-else-in-icjs-preliminary-genocide-ruling/0000018d-4739-d02c-a79f-47bb34a90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队任命周四在加沙地带战斗中丧生的以色列国防军预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/israeli-army-names-idf-reservist-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-thursday/0000018d-4790-d35c-a39f-efda5d230000</link><description>中士。埃利兰·耶格尔 (Eliran Yeger) 少校，36 岁，来自特拉维夫，在加沙地带南部的战斗中身亡。 “埃利兰确实是一位伟大的父亲，他正在努力成为一名更好的父亲。我觉得这是最大的悲伤，”他的遗孀在接受采访时说道</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:14:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/israeli-army-names-idf-reservist-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-thursday/0000018d-4790-d35c-a39f-efda5d230000</guid></item><item><title>当地档案馆偶然发现了德国犹太人被驱逐的秘密拍摄照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/secretly-captured-images-of-german-jews-expulsion-found-by-chance-in-local-archive/0000018d-425b-dc44-a5bf-caff994d0000</link><description>这些照片是由一位犹太业余摄影师冒着生命危险秘密拍摄的，展示了德国布雷斯劳市犹太人被驱逐的情景，这些照片在国际大屠杀纪念日之前首次曝光</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 20:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/secretly-captured-images-of-german-jews-expulsion-found-by-chance-in-local-archive/0000018d-425b-dc44-a5bf-caff994d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯播出三名以色列人质在加沙被囚禁的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-three-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-captivity/0000018d-473c-d02c-a79f-47bf122b0000</link><description>在视频中，30 岁的兽医护士 Doron Steinbrecher 和 19 岁的以色列国防军士兵 Daniela Gilboa 和 Karina Ariav 表示，他们已被囚禁 107 天</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 19:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-three-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-captivity/0000018d-473c-d02c-a79f-47bf122b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谴责国际法院考虑种族灭绝；沙特称以色列“违反”联合国规则，美国称其“毫无根据”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-icj-genocide-mull-u-s-labels-it-unfounded-saudis-note-violations/0000018d-46e2-d35c-a39f-eefaac3f0000</link><description>以色列政治领导人一致谴责法院考虑种族灭绝指控，而巴勒斯坦总理则宣称，“以色列逃避惩罚的日子已经结束了”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 18:57:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-icj-genocide-mull-u-s-labels-it-unfounded-saudis-note-violations/0000018d-46e2-d35c-a39f-eefaac3f0000</guid></item><item><title>2014年，内塔尼亚胡就哈马斯屠杀阴谋发出预警。九年后，10 月 7 日发生了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-netanyahu-forewarned-of-a-hamas-massacre-plot-nine-years-later-oct-7-happened/0000018d-4591-d02c-a79f-479bf39c0000</link><description>2014年加沙行动前不久，以色列领导人获悉以色列南部计划进行大屠杀，并绑架士兵和平民作为讨价还价的筹码。一名以色列国防军将军当时告诉他的同事，“我不想在周六早上报告五个基布兹已被占领”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:57:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-netanyahu-forewarned-of-a-hamas-massacre-plot-nine-years-later-oct-7-happened/0000018d-4591-d02c-a79f-479bf39c0000</guid></item><item><title>优先考虑人质的以色列人是真正理性的声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-who-prioritize-the-hostages-are-the-real-voice-of-reason/0000018d-467f-d02c-a79f-47ff7e620000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-who-prioritize-the-hostages-are-the-real-voice-of-reason/0000018d-467f-d02c-a79f-47ff7e620000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院在国际法院就种族灭绝案向以色列发出警告。这就是内塔尼亚胡应该担心的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/icj-fires-israel-a-warning-shot-over-genocide-case-this-is-why-netanyahu-should-worry/0000018d-4625-dc44-a5bf-ceb7d5cf0000</link><description>国际法院周五的临时裁决给以色列带来了好坏参半的消息：尽管以色列没有被告知在加沙停火，但其命令可能会给以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和他的极右翼部长带来严重的头痛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 15:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/icj-fires-israel-a-warning-shot-over-genocide-case-this-is-why-netanyahu-should-worry/0000018d-4625-dc44-a5bf-ceb7d5cf0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院裁定以色列必须避免在加沙实施种族灭绝行为，不得下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/icj-rules-israel-must-avoid-genocidal-acts-in-gaza-stops-short-of-ordering-cease-fire/0000018d-4606-d35c-a39f-ee5e5b7e0000</link><description>尽管此案的最终裁决可能需要数年时间，但以色列必须履行法院下令的六项临时措施，以保护加沙的巴勒斯坦人，包括提供援助和惩罚煽动种族灭绝的行为</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 15:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/icj-rules-israel-must-avoid-genocidal-acts-in-gaza-stops-short-of-ordering-cease-fire/0000018d-4606-d35c-a39f-ee5e5b7e0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院裁定以色列必须“采取一切措施”避免在加沙发生种族灭绝行为、煽动行为，但不下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/top-un-court-hands-down-preliminary-ruling-in-south-africa-genocide-case-against-israel/0000018d-451e-dc44-a5bf-cdbeb41c0000</link><description>国际法院初步裁决没有下令停止加沙战争，称以色列必须采取一切措施保护平民，惩罚煽动行为。内塔尼亚胡：法院维护以色列自卫权是正确的，但不应该辩论种族灭绝指控</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 10:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/top-un-court-hands-down-preliminary-ruling-in-south-africa-genocide-case-against-israel/0000018d-451e-dc44-a5bf-cdbeb41c0000</guid></item><item><title>从否认大屠杀到所有人的大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/from-holocaust-denial-to-everyone-gets-their-own-revisionism-and-relativism-after-oct-7/0000018d-44be-d02c-a79f-47bfbbf80000</link><description>大屠杀的去犹太化和普遍化不可避免地意味着它后来将成为殴打犹太人自己的一根棍子。那些将 10 月 7 日描述为“另一场大屠杀”的人并不好得多</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 09:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/from-holocaust-denial-to-everyone-gets-their-own-revisionism-and-relativism-after-oct-7/0000018d-44be-d02c-a79f-47bfbbf80000</guid></item><item><title>美国与以色列建立渠道寻求加沙战争平民死亡问题的答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/u-s-establishes-channel-with-israel-to-seek-answers-on-civilian-deaths-in-gaza-war/0000018d-44a1-dc44-a5bf-ccb744f50000</link><description>据哈马斯卫生部称，以色列针对哈马斯的行动造成了巨大伤亡，拜登政府面临越来越大的压力，此次行动已造成超过 25,000 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 08:14:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/u-s-establishes-channel-with-israel-to-seek-answers-on-civilian-deaths-in-gaza-war/0000018d-44a1-dc44-a5bf-ccb744f50000</guid></item></channel></rss>